Name: There's Poop In My Soup
About the game: Have you ever wanted to poop on people but were too shy to just go for it? There's poop in my soup lets you do just that, poop in soups, poop on people, poop on poodles, poop anywhere you please, from the streets of New York to Paris to Beijing. Make sure to tick off that to-poo list and unlock special poo abilities.
